<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ي ق ظ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٥٧٥٣ - ي ق ظ]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>يقَّظَ ييقِّظ، تيقيظًا، فهو مُيقِّظ، والمفعول مُيقَّظ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• يقَّظَه:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>١ - أيقظه؛ أفاقه <span class="c1">"يقَّظتِ الأمُّ طفلَها من نومه"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٢ - نبّهه وحذّره <span class="c1">"يقّظه ممّا يدور حولَه من مؤامرات"</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">• يقَّظَ الشَّيءَ:</span> أثاره وهيّجه <span class="c1">"يقّظ الفتنةََ"</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>